headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid ZBH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Zimmer Biomet’s stock price fell to $99.27. Shareholders have lost 6.1% of their capital, which is disappointing considering the S&P 500 has climbed by 7.6%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
